songs.title: Champions Remix
songs.lyrics:
[Intro: Travis Scott]
Yeah

[Chorus: Both, Travis Scott]
1500, all in singles (Straight up)
Throw it up, watch it fall and drop
Round and round we go (Straight up, straight)
Round and round we go
Champions, we run the city
Number one, they fallin' from the top
Round and round we go
Round and round we go

[Verse: Teyana Taylor]
He said pray for 'em
Get these bitches out the way for 'em
First lady go cray for 'em
So I loaded up the AK for 'em
Hit it down with my head down
Green Jeep with the loud sounds
Deep bass with the mean brow
Do they get what I see now?
Pray for me, put your one hand in the air for me
Anna Wintour need a chair to see how they stare with the bangs and hair for me
It's like they ain't care for me, soul's life is a spare for me
It's like who ain't for care for me, man who's life is to spare for me
I've been getting money where the hell you been now?
Now I'm about as, somehow I was getting paid out
Leave me out here, if it's no tree then it's no shade out
1500 golden trophies on this bitch a champion

[Chorus: Both, Travis Scott & Teyana Taylor]
1500, all in singles (Straight up, own the city)
Throw it up (Throw it up), watch it fall and drop
Round and round we go (Straight up, straight up)
Round and round we go (Oh)
Champions, we run the city
Number one, they fallin' from the top
Round and round we go
Round and round we go (Go)

[Outro: Teyana Taylor]
Own the city
Throw it up, watch it fall and drop
Round and round we go
Champions, we run the city
Number one, they fallin' from the top
Round and round we go
Go
